.slack","typeVersion":2.3,"position":[6534,1420],"id":"8891e47c-a73c-4d8b-b21f-bc307ff56c0a","name":"Escalate Failure to Slack","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000},{"parameters":{"content":"### Hourly Schedule\n\nStarts the workflow on a timer — every 6 h. No input data; downstream nodes fetch what they need.\n\nNext: Keep Valid Emails","width":280,"height":232,"color":5},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-330,520],"id":"b4cb0609-f460-561d-7122-fd87da80f28d","name":"Note: Hourly Schedule"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Keep Valid Emails\n\nDrops items that fail the condition; only qualifying items continue (no false branch).\n\nNext: Score the Lead","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-6,520],"id":"4ac41f8f-4e35-e29b-db52-85126207c9e0","name":"Note: Keep Valid Emails"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Score the Lead\n\nCustom JavaScript: Score each email 0-100 from simple heuristics\n\nNext: Assign Round-Robin Owner","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,520],"id":"708bba0b-8ddb-dba3-fe90-bf0cdca52811","name":"Note: Score the Lead"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Assign Round-Robin Owner\n\nCustom JavaScript: Round-robin owner assignment\n\nNext: Route by Heat","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[642,520],"id":"750cee7a-0fa5-d8c6-e47f-219da92cb0cd","name":"Note: Assign Round-Robin Owner"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Route by Heat\n\nRoutes each item to one of 3 lanes: hot, warm + fallback.\n\nPorts: ①→ Hot → Notion + Instant Ping · ②→ Warm → Drip via Slack · ③→ Cold → Park in Nurture List","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[966,520],"id":"c1f10431-4557-93e0-087a-030a94887998","name":"Note: Route by Heat"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Hot → Notion + Instant Ping\n\nnotion — `create` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Notify Assigned Owner · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Notion integration token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1290,40],"id":"b319b7f9-c6e2-d4a8-0a92-bcd385140687","name":"Note: Hot → Notion + Instant Ping"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Notify Assigned Owner\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Combine Lead Paths · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1938,40],"id":"4bef2337-4cd6-4ad8-9c89-86beb0361d46","name":"Note: Notify Assigned Owner"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Warm → Drip via Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Combine Lead Paths · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2262,520],"id":"84956bb9-001f-40e7-5978-b330556f3806","name":"Note: Warm → Drip via Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Cold → Park in Nurture List\n\nnotion — `create` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Combine Lead Paths · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Notion integration token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2586,1000],"id":"15c38da8-7e9f-bf5c-19bc-bef8e1a42999","name":"Note: Cold → Park in Nurture List"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Combine Lead Paths\n\nRejoins 3 branches into one stream (mode: append) so downstream logic runs once.\n\nNext: Guard Non-Empty from","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3558,520],"id":"d56789fd-2c1e-10fc-cf18-69d3104fe680","name":"Note: Combine Lead Paths"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Guard Non-Empty from\n\nDrops items that fail the condition; only qualifying items continue (no false branch).\n\nNext: Sort Emails Newest First","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4854,520],"id":"b7dc7ee3-91cf-276e-577f-1c75fceaf1ed","name":"Note: Guard Non-Empty from"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Sort Emails Newest First\n\nOrders items (newest first) so limits and digests pick the most relevant records.\n\nNext: Align Field Names","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5178,520],"id":"446c2137-fb39-c489-5568-3badcaa18167","name":"Note: Sort Emails Newest First"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Align Field Names\n\nNormalizes field names so every source feeds the same downstream schema.\n\nNext: Save Execution Metadata","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5502,520],"id":"1e6f49b1-6fea-36be-7271-f7ce781dc9a9","name":"Note: Align Field Names"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Save Execution Metadata\n\nSaves key fields onto the execution record — searchable later in n8n's execution list.\n\nNext: Summarize Run Stats","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5826,520],"id":"53aea200-87fb-56f6-9b90-211019c1b08f","name":"Note: Save Execution Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Summarize Run Stats\n\nShapes the item: writes `runAt`, `itemCount`, `status`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Append Audit Row (Notion)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6150,520],"id":"53f30ced-17b2-e542-0a16-e53bcb112053","name":"Note: Summarize Run Stats"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Append Audit Row (Notion)\n\nnotion — `create` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Send Summary to Twilio · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Notion integration token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6474,520],"id":"2c71e582-69b8-74a9-7bf7-89a60819a24e","name":"Note: Append Audit Row (Notion)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Send Summary to Twilio\n\ntwilio — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Twilio SID + token","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6798,520],"id":"26f8d606-8471-f9fa-ccbd-0e2408042974","name":"Note: Send Summary to Twilio"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Capture Failure Context\n\nShapes the item: writes `failedNode`, `errorMessage`, `workflow`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Escalate Failure to Slack","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6150,1540],"id":"a0275ce6-f24f-1677-b73c-160bc16792ff","name":"Note: Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Escalate Failure to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6474,1540],"id":"ee5407af-0333-ad63-019f-d3f4a507d5fb","name":"Note: Escalate Failure to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"# Onboard subscribers with Notion and Twilio without manual work\n\n**Pattern:** Drip Sequence · **Level:** Advanced · **Trigger:** Scheduled\n\n## What it does\nOnboard subscribers with Notion and Twilio without manual work. It runs automatically on a schedule.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual drip campaigns is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nHourly Schedule → Keep Valid Emails → Score the Lead → Assign Round-Robin Owner → Route by Heat → Hot → Notion + Instant Ping → Notify Assigned Owner → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to drip sequence without manual effort\n- Anyone automating drip campaigns in marketing\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Standardizes the process every time\n- Has retries and error handling built in\n- Responds in seconds\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: Notion integration token; Slack OAuth2; Twilio SID + token.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.","width":480,"height":900},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,80],"id":"a0e8542a-5dec-ef19-ad0e-676f270d68b2","name":"📘 Workflow Overview"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛟 Error handling & retries\n\nExternal calls retry **3× with 2s backoff**. Anything still failing exits through its node's error output into the red error rail → context is captured and the on-call channel is alerted. Set an n8n **Error Workflow** in settings as the final safety net.","width":360,"height":260,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-230,-500],"id":"37ba0083-e7e8-93c3-ccac-6ad05c825590","name":"🛟 Error handling & retries"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your drip campaigns process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.","width":360,"height":260,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[190,-500],"id":"7ad82754-e190-def3-6ba5-8089dbfb8627","name":"🛠 Customize me"}],"connections":{"Hourly Schedule":{"main":[[{"node":"Keep Valid Emails","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Keep Valid Emails":{"main":[[{"node":"Score the Lead","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Score the Lead":{"main":[[{"node":"Assign Round-Robin Owner","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Assign Round-Robin Owner":{"main":[[{"node":"Route by Heat","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Hot → Notion + Instant Ping":{"main":[[{"node":"Notify Assigned Owner","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Route by Heat":{"main":[[{"node":"Hot → Notion + Instant Ping","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Warm → Drip via Slack","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Cold → Park in Nurture List","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Notify Assigned Owner":{"main":[[{"node":"Combine Lead Paths","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Warm → Drip via Slack":{"main":[[{"node":"Combine Lead Paths","type":"main","index":1}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Cold → Park in Nurture List":{"main":[[{"node":"Combine Lead Paths","type":"main","index":2}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Combine Lead Paths":{"main":[[{"node":"Guard Non-Empty from","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Guard Non-Empty from":{"main":[[{"node":"Sort Emails Newest First","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Sort Emails Newest First":{"main":[[{"node":"Align Field Names","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Align Field Names":{"main":[[{"node":"Save Execution Metadata","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Save Execution Metadata":{"main":[[{"node":"Summarize Run Stats","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Summarize Run Stats":{"main":[[{"node":"Append Audit Row (Notion)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Append Audit Row (Notion)":{"main":[[{"node":"Send Summary to Twilio","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Capture Failure Context":{"main":[[{"node":"Escalate Failure to Slack","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Send Summary to Twilio":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]}},"